          "description": "Avoid this disgusting place at all costs.  I asked the nurse a question she responded with an attitude stating she just came back from lunch.  The other staff members are talking on their phones laughing and joking a round in the er.  In addition that same nurse took vitals, blood work never came back for the urine.  This hospital is un clean unsanitary.  Nurses and doctors are discussing patients private info in the hallway.  Today was a slow day for this hospital\u2019s very little patients.  Certainly no reason for a nurse to be on edge about a question.  Never again.",
